snippet.title: Tetradome - Annoucement teaser EN
snippet.description:
Tetradome is a non-linear puzzle adventure where you will have to unravel the  enigmas of the 4 elements if you want to escape from the dome.

Add to your wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3191420/Tetradome/
